
h1. apex-VIES

apex-VIES provides a simple API to validate EU VAT Numbers using the VIES VAT number validation WebService http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/vieshome.do

h2. How to use apex-VIES API


h3. Checking VAT Numbers


the API returns VIES.VATCheck wrapper objects holding all information
<code>
	// submit a complete VATId for validation
	VIES.VATCheck checkResult = VIES.checkVAT('DE812639372');

	//you can submit country Code and vatNumber seperatly
	checkResult = VIES.checkVAT('DE','812639372');

</code>


h3. Utils

Splitting a VAT ID into countryCode and vatNumber

<code>
	VIES.splitVATID('DE812639372');
</code>


VIES FAQ http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/faqvies.do